               Well, you know, the usual; The Federal 
               Reserve, the rainforest.
 
               Cynthia thought we should nuke the rainforest, you know, get 
               rid of it in one
 
               fell swoop so we can at least eliminate it as a subject of conversation. 
               What
 
               about you?

               
