               for George, you are dead wrong.
 
               Dead wrong. Who is she?

               
                             ELAINE
               Who is he?

               
                             JERRY
               He's George!

               
                             ELAINE
               She's Cynthia!

               
                             JERRY
               So what?

               
                             ELAINE
               What, you don't think she's beautiful?
 
               
               
                             JERRY
               I don't know, what's with the eyebrows?
 
               
               
                             ELAINE
               You know what your problem is? Your 
               standards are too high.
 
               
                             JERRY
               I went out with you.

               
